headline: LEN Q4 Deep Dive: Margin Pressures Persist as Lennar Reinforces Efficiency Initiatives
summary: Homebuilder Lennar (NYSE:LEN) reported revenue ahead of Wall Streets expectations in Q4 CY2025, but sales fell by 5.8% year on year to $9.37 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.03 per share was 6.8% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
